www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/End-of-the-rad@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/End-of-the-rad@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/End-of-the-rad@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/End-of-the-rad@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/End-of-the-rad@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2025 年路尽头的第一批艺术家名单已经公布，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/father-john-misty">Father John Misty</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/caribou">Caribou</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/self-esteem">Self Esteem</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sharon-van-etten">Sharon Van Etten 和 The Attachment Theory 等</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/end-of-the-road-festival-review-photos-2023-wet-leg-3492779">2023 年路尽头节：一场公共奇观</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>该节日定于明年夏天在多塞特郡的拉默树花园举行，并将于 8 月 28 日至 31 日期间举行。</p><p>今天（12 月 5 日），添加到该法案中的名字已得到确认，所有四位头条人物都被锁定。其中包括电子制作人 Caribou，他将带来一套庆祝其新舞池专辑《Honey》发行的演出。 &#39;。这也是他继 15 年前在 Big Top 首次亮相后，在音乐节上的最新亮相。</p><p>同时宣布成为头条新闻的还有谢菲尔德歌手 Self Esteem，她将在 2025 年将她标志性的肯定生命的流行音乐和独立音乐融合在一起带到主舞台。这一消息发布之际，她分享了一首名为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/self-esteem-shares-vulnerable-new-b-side-love-second-music-first-3793452">“Love Second Music First”</a>的反思性新单曲（ 9 月推出当前单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/self-esteem-and-moonchild-sanelly-team-up-for-gender-bending-new-single-big-man-3767159">《Big Man》</a>的 B 面，这是她自 2021 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">全英音乐奖</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">水星奖</a>提名专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/self-esteem-prioritise-pleasure-review-3069775">《Prioritise Pleasure》</a>以来的第一首新作品。</p><p>约翰·米斯蒂神父也已得到确认，他的名字被添加到该法案中，是因为他最近推出了新专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/father-john-misty-mahashmashana-review-3814237">Mahashmashana</a> 》，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/father-john-misty-announces-uk-and-ireland-tour-for-summer-2025-tickets-3818499">宣布将于 2025 年 6 月和 8 月进行英国和爱尔兰巡演。</a>演员 Sharon Van Etten 将与她的新乐队 The Attachment Theory 一起表演。这一消息发布之际，他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-van-etten-the-attachment-theory-launch-epic-single-afterlife-self-titled-debut-album-uk-european-tour-3805610">分享了即将在新年发行的首张同名专辑的消息</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDMUxxqN-2M/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.