Road 2024 见证了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idles">IDLES</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slowdive">Slowdive</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fever-ray">Fever Ray</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sleater-kinney">Sleater-Kinney</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yo-la-tengo">Yo La Tengo</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lankum">Lankum</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jockstrap">Jockstrap</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">CMAT</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nation-of-language">Nation Of Language</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-lemon-twigs">The Lemon Twigs</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Richard-Hawley">Richard Hawley</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Lambrini-Girls">Lambrini Girls</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Alt%C4%B1n-G%C3%BCn">Altın Gün</a>等乐队的表演。</p><p>在此之前，2023 年版《路尽头》的表演包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">《最后的晚宴》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/be-your-owen-pet">《做你自己的宠物》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/animal-collective">《动物集体</a>的熊猫》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/picture-parlour">《Picture Parlor》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/geese">《鹅》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/king-gizzard-and-the-wizard-lizard">《砂王王和蜥蜴巫师》的</a>表演，以及独立超级明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wet-leg">Wet</a>的秘密老虎机<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wet-leg">腿</a>。</p><p> <em>NME</em>在对 2023 年《End Of The Road》的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/end-of-the-road-festival-review-photos-2023-wet-leg-3492779">五星级评论</a>中写道：“世界上最好的音乐节？也许吧——但请保密。这篇评论将在五年内自毁……”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/end-of-the-road-2025-line-up-headlined-by-father-john-misty-caribou-self-esteem-sharon-van-etten-the-attachment-theory-3819119">由Father John Misty、Caribou、Self Esteem、Sharon Van Etten 和 The Attachment Theory 领衔的《End Of The Road 2025》阵容</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
